expression.expression-string: "select (select count(distinct i.CERTIFICATE) from tb_ic_operate@db69 i,tb_global_person_certificate@db69 p where i.CERTIFICATE=p.CERTIFICATE_NUMBER and i.OPERATION_VEHICLENO != replace(p.PLATE_NUMBER,'.','')) as COUNT, tt.* from (select t.*, rownum as rn from (select distinct i.CERTIFICATE,i.OPERATION_VEHICLENO,p.CERTIFICATE_NUMBER,p.PLATE_NUMBER,p.NAME from tb_ic_operate@db69 i,tb_global_person_certificate@db69 p where i.CERTIFICATE=p.CERTIFICATE_NUMBER and i.OPERATION_VEHICLENO != replace(p.PLATE_NUMBER,'.','')order by i.OPERATION_VEHICLENO, p.NAME desc) t where rownum <= 20)tt where tt.rn >0"

"select VEHICLE_NO,count(VEHICLE_NO) COUNT,g.area_name from (select to_char(CATCH_TIME, 'yyyy-mm-dd') CATCH_TIME,vehicle_no from tb_hk_not_online@db69 where 1=1 and VEHICLE_NO = '浙AB9219' and CATCH_TIME >= TO_DATE('2019-05-01 00:00:00','yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') and CATCH_TIME <= TO_DATE('2019-05-28 23:59:59','yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss')) ol left join (select plate_number,area_name from tb_global_vehicle@db69 where BUSINESS_SCOPE_NAME='客运：出租车客运。' AND STATUS_NAME='营运' AND PLATE_NUMBER LIKE '浙A%') g on ol.vehicle_no=g.plate_number where 1=1 group by vehicle_no, g.area_name order by vehicle_no"

" select v.*,to_char(r.RR_TIME,'yyyy-MM-dd hh24:mi:ss') TIME from tb_repair_record@db69 r left join (SELECT distinct VEHI_NO,VEHI_NUM,COMP_NAME,VEHI_SIM,HOME_TEL,NIGHT_TEL,OWN_NAME,MT_NAME,MDT_SUB_TYPE from VW_VEHICLE@db69) v on v.VEHI_NO=r.VEHI_NO where r.VEHI_NO <> ' ' and r.RR_TIME >=to_date('2019-02-25 00:00:00','yyyy-MM-dd hh24:mi:ss') and r.RR_TIME <=to_date('2019-02-25 23:59:59','yyyy-MM-dd hh24:mi:ss') order by r.RR_TIME desc"
